   MODIS First Light


   New Realease Image
     __________________________________________________________________

   For more information on the following new features please see
   http://daac.gsfc.nasa.gov/CAMPAIGN_DOCS/MODIS/new.shtml

New Products Released

     * MOD28M MODIS/Terra Sea Surface Temperature QC'd Params 1-4 Monthly
       L3 Global 4km ISEAG
     * MODOCM MODIS/Terra Ocean Color QC'd Composite Params 1-36 Monthly
       L3 Global 4km ISEAG

New Search and Order Features

   Recently several new features have been added to the Goddard Search and
   Order Interface, a.k.a.,WHOM:
     * Attribute Filtering.
     * Ocean Level 3 parameter "subsetting".
     * On-demand channel/band subsetting.

New Tools and Services Page

     * We have added some tools that we think are most useful to users of
       MODIS data. You can always find information about tools and
       services on our Tools and Services web page by following the
       "Tools" link on our menu bar.

   Additional MODIS products and their release dates can be found in the
   history log.
